'''豆血红蛋白'''（{{lang-en|Leghemoglobin}}，也称为“豆科血红素”，legoglobin）是一类在[[荚果|豆类]]植物的{{le|根瘤|root nodule}}中参与[[固氮作用|固氮作用]]的{{link-en|血红素蛋白|Hemeprotein}}。它是由这些植物的[[根|根]]在被固氮细菌定殖后产生的，这一类细菌称为“[[根瘤菌|根瘤菌]]”。这是一种植物和细菌相互[[共生|共生]]的关系：没有[[根瘤菌属|根瘤菌属]]（''Rhizobium''）细菌定殖，[[大豆|大豆]]的根不会合成豆血红蛋白。豆血红蛋白在化学和结构上类似于[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]的[[血红蛋白|血红蛋白]]，并且因含有[[血基質|血基質]]也呈红色。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Nadler KD, Avissar YJ | title = Heme Synthesis in Soybean Root Nodules: I. On the Role of Bacteroid delta-Aminolevulinic Acid Synthase and delta-Aminolevulinic Acid Dehydrase in the Synthesis of the Heme of Leghemoglobin | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_plant-physiology_1977-09_60_3/page/433 | journal = Plant Physiology | volume = 60 | issue = 3 | pages = 433–6 | date = September 1977 | pmid = 16660108 | pmc = 542631 | doi = 10.1104/pp.60.3.433 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = O'Brian MR, Kirshbom PM, Maier RJ | title = Bacterial heme synthesis is required for expression of the leghemoglobin holoprotein but not the apoprotein in soybean root nodules | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 84 | issue = 23 | pages = 8390–3 | date = December 1987 | pmid = 3479799 | pmc = 299548 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.84.23.8390 | bibcode = 1987PNAS...84.8390O }}</ref>

